        "title": "How not to use escape character in java",
        "body": "<p>I have to use \\\" in a string but apparently, I cant. \nTo be more specific I need to do something like:\nLet's say the string is something like: <\/p>\n\n<p><code>I like cookie's \"%s\"<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p><code>str = str.replace('\"', '\\\"');<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>But I need the string to look like this after the replace : <\/p>\n\n<p><code>I Like cookie's \\\"%s\\\"<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>Is anyone willing to help?<\/p>\n",
